{
  "stem": "26728.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And God it just gives me cold chills to think about that, that-- that-- The feeling was, you know, of-- of a mixture of rage and-- and frustration and why can't I-- why can't we do something?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, there's-- you-- you want to do something physical, because that's what we're used to doing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Phys-- guys like him and I, you're used to doing physical stuff.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So you want to do something physical.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And what the heck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Go do-- go do something physical.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we-- we got out of there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I couldn't talk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I told his guy, I said, I, you know, this is getting to be heavy duty for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he said, well, let's go back to the main part of the camp then.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, then things have quieted down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we're coming down this street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there's a wall about this high.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it goes clear around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this turned out to be the hospital, which I didn't know at the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it goes-- we're here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the wall is here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there's an intersection, and then the wall continues like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So we're about 40 feet or so from the corner when we hear this machine gun fire.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it was an American 30 caliber automatic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I could identify it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it sounded like two of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So I said jeez, stop this jeep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There's-- they're having a shoot out someplace.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I got out of the jeep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I crawled on the ground to the corner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I peeked around the corner, because that's where the sound was coming from.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And here's a machine gun in the middle of the street, but just-- just, you know, not enough for two cars.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
